div.div: Note that the composite displays like Wave12I48 should inject Epd4Spi. The magic happens in update() where the SPI master data is redirecting the pixel buffer to different SPI slave controllers on each epaper. This abstracts all the complexity letting you treat the eink as a single Epd.
